title: Hill, Warwickshire
text: Hill is a <a href="hamlet%20%28place%29">hamlet</a> in the <a href="civil%20parish">civil parish</a> of <a href="Leamington%20Hastings">Leamington Hastings</a> and the <a href="Rugby%20%28borough%29">borough of Rugby</a>, in <a href="Warwickshire">Warwickshire</a>, England. The hamlet is between Leamington Hastings and the <a href="A426%20road">A426 road</a> from <a href="Rugby%2C%20Warwickshire">Rugby</a> to <a href="Southam">Southam</a>.
